Show Bash current state:ph_check_app_name -s -a Bash | more
Show Bash run account:ph_get_app_user Bash
Start or switch to Bash:startbash.sh | more
Stop Bash:stopbash.sh force | more
Restart Bash:restartbash.sh | more
Install Bash and integrate with PieHelper:confapps_ps.sh -p inst -a Bash
Update Bash to the latest version (only if installed as a package):ph_update_pkg $PH_BASH_PKG_NAME | more
Configure Bash:confapps_ph.sh -p conf -a Bash
Go to the OptsManagement for Bash submenu:ph_show_menu OptsManagement_Bash
Go to the TTYManagement for Bash submenu:ph_show_menu TTYManagement_Bash
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Open Shell to home directory (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Return to previous screen:return
